        <p>Locate and select the border-radius property that you want to change. Each corner (bottom-left, bottom-right, top-left, top-right) can be set separately (e.g., border-bottom-left-radius, border-top-right-radius). Even better, you can set the main <span class="Emphasis">border-radius</span> property, which lets you specify the amount of curve for all four corners in one place.</p>
